Class ReiseTableConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • reiseplugin.gui.ReiseTableConfig

  • public class ReiseTableConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the ReiseTableConfig.Model and the ReiseTableConfig.Renderer for the JTable representing the calculated results.
